        "subject": "LU-709 build: cleanup LC_FS_RENAME_DOES_D_MOVE/SPLICE_READ",
        "message": "LU-709 build: cleanup LC_FS_RENAME_DOES_D_MOVE/SPLICE_READ\n\n1. FS_RENAME_DOES_D_MOVE is defined since v2.6.19\n   and RHEL5 v2.6.18 back ported it\n2. file_operations.sendfile was changed to splice_read since\n   v2.6.23 but RHEL5 v2.6.18 has them both. So all kernels that\n   Lustre supports have .splice_read\n\nSigned-off-by: Peng Tao <peng_tao@emc.com>\nChange-Id: Id72ac8f17227faed0c8380421c9f02bf261dfd6a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
